VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'more. So, let\'s jump right in. First up, this AI is pretty cool. So, Tencent just released Hunuan World Voyager and this creates a 3D world from just a single reference image. So, here are some'

[01:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'examples. Notice that the user can specify the camera path to control how to move across the scene. Now, we\'ve seen other so-called game generators before, like Google\'s Genie 3 or Tencent'

[01:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
